OL,3,CFarmer admits he 'messed up' over
OL,4,Cdeath of son by reversing over him
OL,6,FA farmer who killed his three-year-old
OL,7,Fson when he reversed over him in a
OL,8,Fdefective farm vehicle broke down in
OL,9,Ftears as he gave evidence at his
OL,10,Ftrial, saying: "I messed up... I made
OL,11,Fa mistake."
OL,13,FNeil Speakman, 39, was operating a
OL,14,Ftelehandler - a machine used to pick
OL,15,Fup wood chippings - at his farm in
OL,16,FBury when he reversed and 'drove over'
OL,17,FAlbie Speakman at around midday on 16
OL,18,FJuly 2022, jurors were previously told.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
