OL,6,FThe telehandler was later inspected by
OL,7,Fhealth and safety inspectors and found
OL,8,Fits various mechanical defects would
OL,9,Fhave hindered safe operation, the
OL,10,Fcourt has heard.
OL,12,FIt concluded, jurors were told, that
OL,13,Fit was "foreseeable that persons in
OL,14,Fthe vicinity of the vehicle could be
OL,15,Finjured or killed when the vehicle was
OL,16,Fworking".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
