OL,3,CFarmer admits he 'messed up' over
OL,4,Cdeath of son by reversing over him
OL,6,FFollowing a break, Mr Speakman added:
OL,7,F"I jumped off the machine, I rushed
OL,8,Fround and I scooped him up in my arms
OL,9,Fbut there was no response."
OL,11,FHe said he ran into the farmhouse and
OL,12,Ftried to perform CPR while a 999 call
OL,13,Fwas made. Mr Speakman said was a
OL,14,F'blur' from that point to taking Albie
OL,15,Fto hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
